sequenceDiagram
    participant Platform as Renewal & Upsell Platform
    participant Bot as AI Agent (Voice / Email)
    participant Customer as End Customer
    participant CSM as Customer Success Manager

    Platform->>Bot: 1. Trigger automated campaign (Renewal / Upsell)
    Bot->>Customer: 2. Outbound engagement (Call or Email)
    
    alt Customer Answers / Engages
        Customer->>Bot: 3. Interacts with the AI Agent
        Bot->>Customer: 4. AI responds dynamically to inquiries or objections
        Customer->>Bot: 5. Expresses intent & sentiment (e.g., Positive / Ready to Renew)
    else Customer Ignores
        Bot->>Platform: Log unresponsiveness / voicemail
    end

    Bot->>Platform: 6. Streams real-time transcript & sentiment data
    
    Platform->>CSM: 7. Push instant WebSocket alerts to CSM dashboard
    Platform->>Platform: 8. Update Account Health & Relationship Score automatically
    
    opt Human Escalation
        CSM->>Customer: 9. Manual follow-up to close deal or resolve high risk
    end
